          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-[.open]:rotate-180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 10l5 5 5-5" stroke-width="2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="m-2 mt-1 toggle-description hidden text-gray-600 transition-all duration-300">
          Estudiante en Prácticas DUAL - CFGS DAM.
        </p>
